              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-1">Pattern insights</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600">AI analysis reveals your unique stress vs. emotional eating patterns over time</p>
            </div>
